## Quick Reference

| Principle       | Do                                                          | Avoid                                              |
| --------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| Async           | `await` every async call, `return await`                    | Floating promises, bare `return promise`           |
| Interfaces      | Small, focused, typed data objects (`data/types/`)          | Multiple raw string parameters                     |
| Guard clauses   | Fail-fast at the top; throw on missing deps                 | Deep `if/else` nesting; silent skips               |
| Duplication     | Lookup maps for key→locator patterns                        | Repeated `if/else if` chains                       |
| Variables       | `const` by default                                          | `let` unless reassignment is needed                |
| Type safety     | `unknown` + type guard                                      | `any`                                              |
| Known values    | Union types                                                 | Raw `string` for constrained params                |
| Env config      | `baseURL` + relative `goto`; `process.env` only in config   | Hard-coded URLs; `process.env` in page objects     |
| Complexity      | Add when needed                                             | Speculative abstractions                           |
| Local variables | Inline if used once; name it only when used 2+ times        | Single-use intermediate variables                  |
| Imports         | Only import what is used                                    | Unused imports or variables                        |
